{"tid":1126660,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"見到心儀男仔玩交友app，你地點睇？","createTime":"2019-04-26T14:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:57:33.000Z","uid":249799,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8c20d909aa20955a0290ded72c5f3872034a31e2","tid":1126660,"uid":249799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"早排識左個男仔，晚晚都有傾電話又第二日照whatsapp(有曖昧成份)<br />\n發現無論諗法、觀點同理念都好相似，以為會好快喺埋一齊<br />\n漸漸已經對佢產生好感，但基於佢性格太忽冷忽熱、難以捉摸(包括有時唔覆機)，所以有半放棄狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />近排都無再同佢contact<br />\n直到早2日我好好奇究竟唔覆機係咪有其他女仔揾佢時候，決定求其down個交友app睇下佢係咪裏面<br />\n點知碌到無幾耐就見到佢，嗰刻直頭好似有舊大石打落我心裏面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見佢已經玩左幾個月(正正就我地每晚傾電話嗰個月到依家)，徹底心已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰app專門係約炮同揾sp，心死原因主要係佢原來一直背住我去識其他女仔，同埋會諗佢會唔會當左我係其中一個女sp(差在未上床)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有依家樂觀d睇好彩我走得快，未俾佢食住<br />\n同憑良心個句希望佢小心d帶眼識女仔，好驚佢會俾壞女仔呃佢感情同金錢<br />\n唔知你地點睇？我應該點走返出黎？"},{"pid":"83a02b528d6e624674efc9f8dcb6b150274d3fdc","tid":1126660,"uid":213649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"Skrout"},{"pid":"92639a74382d71dc405854f501a6d12c7c021cea","tid":1126660,"uid":88036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"點識？"},{"pid":"6c97faa033828b445490d75f63802400cdddfcc7","tid":1126660,"uid":249799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92639a74382d71dc405854f501a6d12c7c021cea","tid":1126660,"uid":88036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"點識？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"fd搭fd識"},{"pid":"390d68e34e02f9deb8f3d2ba967ff01a06d180a2","tid":1126660,"uid":34929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"<em>同憑良心個句希望佢小心d帶眼識女仔，好驚佢會俾壞女仔呃佢感情同金錢</em><br />\n人地呃蝦條都要膽心"},{"pid":"d2e9d8a68b44fa99f4302f4a57a66c7886cae3ac","tid":1126660,"uid":242444,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"你驚自己好過啦<br />\n佢呢啲player點會被女呃"},{"pid":"ede39ea7af43c32e59e84a65c055f93e5627b44d","tid":1126660,"uid":89735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"你擔心個player做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f283e6d5991f7d9ea74d3df574dfba75311772","tid":1126660,"uid":249799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2e9d8a68b44fa99f4302f4a57a66c7886cae3ac","tid":1126660,"uid":242444,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"你驚自己好過啦<br />\n佢呢啲player點會被女呃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"可能仲有少少感情，都唔想睇到佢咁"},{"pid":"d3e3f6fb634d5f8d5a59e6e17f1c8119b81ca235","tid":1126660,"uid":8138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a6f283e6d5991f7d9ea74d3df574dfba75311772","tid":1126660,"uid":249799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2e9d8a68b44fa99f4302f4a57a66c7886cae3ac","tid":1126660,"uid":242444,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"你驚自己好過啦<br />\n佢呢啲player點會被女呃"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"可能仲有少少感情，都唔想睇到佢咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"咩唔想到佢咁<br />\n<br />\n根本就係你溝佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be4e63130fe692bcc4df6c044be4963519ab92c","tid":1126660,"uid":193476,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"十個真男人，十個都會約炮/揾sp/叫雞，其實好普遍。"},{"pid":"5ba908501845b20b707d698b9c97ace8a4da1ea9","tid":1126660,"uid":90403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2